WEBVTT

00:07:29.834 --> 00:07:32.179
so that they can just
take care of that for you.

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:34.204
If that doesn't work,

00:07:35.307 --> 00:07:37.317
maybe you'd consider paying somebody

00:07:37.341 --> 00:07:40.721
to just "unofficially" take care
of it on your behalf --

00:07:40.745 --> 00:07:43.503
especially if you thought
nobody was going to catch you.

00:07:44.790 --> 00:07:47.160
Not out of malice or greed,

00:07:47.184 --> 00:07:50.275
just trying to make sure that you get
something to work for you

00:07:50.299 --> 00:07:51.457
so you can move on.

00:07:51.918 --> 00:07:54.928
Unfortunately, that
is the beginning of corruption.

00:07:55.439 --> 00:07:57.762
And if left to thrive and grow,

00:07:57.786 --> 00:07:59.352
it seeps into the whole system,

00:07:59.376 --> 00:08:00.746
and before you know it,